PrecisEnactment of the EXPORT CONTROL LIST NOTIFICATION REGULATIONS which specify the kind of information and the time frame within which it must be provided to the Minister of the Environment by those who export any substance that appears on the Export Control List set out in Schedule 3 to the Act, effective March 31, 2000.
